headline: MGM: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: LAS VEGAS (AP) — MGM Resorts International (MGM) on Thursday reported fourth-quarter earnings of $293.6 million. The Las Vegas-based company said it had net income of $1.11 per share. Earnings, adjusted for one-time gains and costs, came to $1.60 per share.
